name: Kazi Farms Kitchen Loitta Dried Fish
description:
Kazi Farms Kitchen Loitta Dried Fish comes in a 125 gm package and is made from loitta fish, a type of small freshwater fish commonly found in rivers and ponds in Bangladesh. name: Dhakaiya Mola Shutki
description:
Dhakaiya Mola Shutki 125 gm is a cherished culinary delight that brings the rich and authentic flavors of Bengal to your dining table. This dried and fermented fish is prepared through a meticulous process that preserves its unique taste and texture. Often enjoyed as a side dish or a key ingredient in traditional Bengali recipes, Mola Shutki adds depth and intensity to a variety of dishes.

name: Fargo Safe Dry Fish (Churi Shutki)
description:
Fargo is introducing safe and Organic Churi Dry Fish (from World Bank, IFAD & PKSF supported Safe Dry Fish Project). This quality protein and nutrient-rich sea dry fish has iodine, high-quality protein, OMEGA-3 Fatty Acid, Zinc, Calcium, copper, and selenium. It is natural and hygienically processed with no added preservatives.
